
All pages should have:
    An identical nav bar with links to the other pages (done)
        either vertical or horizontal
    An idential footer, fixed to the bottom of the page (done)
    An idential header, with the fictional company's logo  (done)
        Image or text
    An space for an aside
Landing page:
    The home page should have an introduction to the company (done)
    It should display a banner image with a text description of the company (done)
        Optional: the image should cycle or scroll (done)
About Us Page:
    It should display a series of images with a text box underneath (done)
    The text box should have default text displayed (done)
    If a user mouses over an image, new text should be displayed in the box (done)
    WHen the user leaves the image, the text should revert to the default message (need assistance)
        Optional: Add an animation when a user mouses over an image (done)
Products and Services Page:
    It should display a series of images and text descriptions of products/services (done)
    There should be a "cart" icon that displays the user's current cart and total cost (done)
    Each product/service should have a button that will add it to the cart (done)
    The items in the cart should have a button that will remove it from the cart (done)
        Optional: Implement a search bar for products (done)
    The cart does NOT need to persist
Customers Page:
    It should display a form that will capture a user's input (done)
    The form should capture a user's name, username, email (done)
    The form should have radio buttons for if they want to be on a mailing list (done)
    The form should have a checkbox for what services they are interested in (done)
    Each user should be displayed in a list when the user submits their data
        Optional: implement a search bar for the customers, and add an edit feature
    The customers do NOT need to persist
